{"tid":326720,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有玩過雲起既水滸歷險online","createTime":"2017-07-18T08:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T13:24:34.000Z","uid":129004,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd34b57e94312f21dbcc93623e5a1917d81fb10","tid":326720,"uid":129004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:30:09.000Z","msg":"好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小四公測玩到中五<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人知而家d私服多唔多人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62484c59919da7641a786240eed166c6db635cd","tid":326720,"uid":103271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"留返個美好回憶俾自已，咪玩啦，用而傢既角度望會好差"},{"pid":"cf08ffa0dd6f37177752572ef7a2ed8a60e14d82","tid":326720,"uid":10338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:33:08.000Z","msg":"當年期望過有一日會出晒108個英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d180c2db7dc230972ea1235bed5b2fe7fbc7794","tid":326720,"uid":98556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"果陣好細個<br />\nD點亂鳩咁配<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到隻人去到邊都唔夠打  要係咁搵人帶升<br />\n仲記得有個人送左隻孔明比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b377d69c72d957e8f04d805e615d3b9c4974b4","tid":326720,"uid":129004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留返個美好回憶俾自已，咪玩啦，用而傢既角度望會好差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打玩過？<br />\n試過兩次訓教發夢係玩番呢隻game<br />\n有一次直頭入左隻game玩<br />\n真係好多回憶 <br />\n小學個陣比人昆左兩張點數喊左成晚<br />\n去到中學開始識玩玩到賺勁多錢<br />\n去到最後因為屋企有事要放棄隻game<br />\n當考完DSE之後諗住玩番 但已經執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無得見住隻game最後一秒有d心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b2c9cce1a486ce57f0042f584ef7f7ac289614","tid":326720,"uid":119562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:39:09.000Z","msg":"有 好記得小學日日返屋企玩"},{"pid":"1c1ebce63e42cc7b44823177f1a853012c07b949","tid":326720,"uid":129004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果陣好細個<br />\nD點亂鳩咁配<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到隻人去到邊都唔夠打  要係咁搵人帶升<br />\n仲記得有個人送左隻孔明比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n初時係真係好正<br />\n去到石門有隻史進已經好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到後期玩到成千e錢 都好似不外如是咁"},{"pid":"1e7a5e37992015f0ab1a18a2e177f329e277d208","tid":326720,"uid":129004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:40:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩係到睇私服點開<br />\n有機會同有錢既話我會光復呢隻game<br />\n唔會好似雲起咁剩係識搵人貨金<br />\n做一隻最公平既online game"},{"pid":"80ecfd78d9ed712ded6909078cc558b121e5f4f5","tid":326720,"uid":4557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"玩住熱血水滸囉 幾多人"},{"pid":"836334621ed7711efd54ef84956809d4dabec0a9","tid":326720,"uid":33033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:44:24.000Z","msg":"第一隻online game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c320dba6a09953e4bdb5acd6b4f5e6b453f9596c","tid":326720,"uid":37922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:47:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7f255f18720cf52eba84ecc748f8008ae972181","tid":326720,"uid":129004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩住熱血水滸囉 幾多人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄有無圖cap黎J下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4240e42e83612b52ddb1974dd89aedde078c737","tid":326720,"uid":4557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩住熱血水滸囉 幾多人</blockquote><br />